sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant UI as Student Edit Page
    participant LW as Livewire Component
    participant DB as Database

    User->>UI: Open create/update student page
    UI->>LW: mount(user?)
    LW->>DB: Load student, classes, and related options
    DB-->>LW: Existing values and option lists
    LW-->>UI: Render student form

    User->>UI: Change institute/campus/programme
    UI->>LW: updatedInstituteId()/updatedCampusId()/updatedProgrammeId()
    LW->>DB: Re-query valid dependent options
    DB-->>LW: Filtered classes/programmes/campuses
    LW-->>UI: Re-render dependent fields

    User->>UI: Save student
    UI->>LW: save()
    LW->>DB: Validate and insert/update user + student + class links
    DB-->>LW: Persist completed
    LW-->>UI: Success toast (new: redirect to edit page)
